comments: Wright (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Caldwell-Pope (LAL).
Davis (SAC) makes marginal contact with James' (LAL) body during the pick and does not affect his SQBR.
Holmes (SAC) hangs on the rim and causes the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Schroder (LAL) slightly extends his arm into Davis' (SAC) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the pick.
Davis (SAC) momentarily places his hand to Schroder's (LAL) front during his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact to James' (LAL) body during his upward shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (LAL) swipes down and dislodges the ball from Wright (SAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) maintains a legal pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Davis (LAL) makes contact with Holmes (SAC) that affects his SQBR on the driving shot attempt.
Davis (SAC) absorbs the contact to James' (LAL) arm at the start of his drive.
Hield (SAC) legally contests James' (LAL) driving shot attempt as James initiates the contact by slightly extending his arm to brace for the potential contact.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes marginal contact with Wright's (SAC) body at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Davis (LAL) cleanly blocks Wright (SAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) makes slight contact with Davis' (LAL) arm in the post and does not affect his control of the ball.
Wright (SAC) commits a take foul on James (LAL) prior to gathering the ball.
Davis (LAL) commits a take foul on Haliburton (SAC).
